{"tid":156483,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我仲未忘記佢","createTime":"2017-03-14T18:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T18:41:44.000Z","uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4324ed3328506207218ff179a86de66ba95f4c4d","tid":156483,"uid":68675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"都分手左4個月了(我地都拍左2年幾)<br />\n當時係個男同我講分手先既<br />\n分手個陣又話仲鐘意我<br />\n但其實我到宜家都鐘意佢<br />\n<br />\n佢宜家有女朋友<br />\n前個陣，仲話想同翻我一齊<br />\n但要同左個女仔分手先<br />\n但宜家變左成個月冇再搵我<br />\n<br />\n我唔去諗佢，其實都ok既<br />\n但一接觸到一d容易勾起我和他的回憶的事情時<br />\n我就不自然地想起了他<br />\n<br />\n我仲有少少衝動想揾佢<br />\n但我一直抑壓自己<br />\n<br />\n唔敢搵佢<br />\n因為我怕佢會拒絕我<br />\n<br />\n定係我真係等時間沖淡我對他的感覺？<br />\n<br />\n我係好傻<br />\n人地都唔再搵我<br />\n但我個心仲好掛住佢<br />\n<br />\n唉想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5db6976bbc3c99cf0295630748cc44e2fe0039a","tid":156483,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"一點一點地刺激你<br />\n他覺得這樣很好玩<br />\n因為你死心塌地"},{"pid":"5a24cd3ea7e148e9fba4aca2e740bffd71e3ae77","tid":156483,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:21:05.000Z","msg":"後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488663e8b596d87411cd5a7e9dce5327eb52cdb0","tid":156483,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"佢散左咪會再黎搵你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf79b26427b721b874a089c1f249f5bc577f6843","tid":156483,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢散左咪會再黎搵你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者鳩痕果時都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c5ec57140fa6914